title: Tale of Four Cities: Toronto - Converse CONS
description:
Tale of Four Cities explores the skate communities within the four cities that CONS Project takes place-- Boston, Toronto, Los Angeles and New York. This film follows CONS skate ambassadors while they visit some of the Toronto's best skate spots, shops, hangouts, and the community surrounding them.

Directed by Richard Quintero
